# 🗂️ File Organizer

A lightweight Python script that helps you automatically organize the messy contents of a folder (like your Downloads directory) into categorized subfolders based on file types.

## ✅ Features

- Sorts files into folders like `Images`, `Documents`, `Videos`, `Music`, `Archives`, etc.
- Supports custom folder paths.
- Handles unknown file types by putting them into a `Others` folder.
- Easy to modify and extend for personal needs.

## 🚀 How to Use

1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/file-organizer.git
   cd file-organizer
